\tau_{t,s}:T_{\gamma(s)}M\to T_{\gamma(t)}M
F(t)=g(\gamma(t))(\tau_{t,s} X(\gamma(s)), \tau_{t,s}  Y(\gamma(s))).
F'(s)=g(\gamma(t))\left(\frac{d}{dt}\bigg|_{t=s}\tau_{t,s}  X(\gamma(s)),  \tau_{t,s}Y(\gamma(s))\right)+g(\gamma(t))\left(\frac{d}{dt}\bigg|_{t=s}\tau_{t,s}  Y(\gamma(s)), \tau_{t,s}X(\gamma(s))\right)+\dot\gamma\left[g(X,Y)\right](\gamma(s)) \ (\star).
